<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1910/523452-625x416.jpg" alt="MamaMagic celebrates its 50th expo" width="625" height="416">Having won numerous awards over the years, in 2018 MamaMagic Cape Town won Best Exhibition of the Year at the AAXO ROAR Awards. Since its’ first baby expo in 2005, the brand has welcomed over 1.2 million visitors through the doors. It is the ideal platform to connect with moms, the key decision maker in the household. With SA’s largest baby store, Baby City as a retail partner, the expo offers innovative products, special offers, expert advice and Barney, the world’s most-loved dinosaur. MamaMagic is the place to connect with South African families.